# Skirmisher
Skirmishers are mobile combatants with a vast amount of knowledge of how best to utilize terrain to their advantage. Their vast understanding of the lay of the land gives them unique bonuses in combat that they can use to swing the tides of battle in their favor. Even when in terrain they find otherwise foreign, they still feel in their element.

Regardless of their acuity of the land, they're swift fighters, able to strike with multiple different weapons easily, even in the thick of battle.

